# ORIG TITLE    Filin says ‘wait and see’ for acid attacker . 
# ORIG CONTENT  The artistic director of the Bolshoi ballet Sergei Filin has left hospital in Moscow bound for specialist treatment in Germany to try and save his sight. Filin has said he knows who attacked him with acid last month, but is refusing to talk for now until investigators make an announcement. He said he remains optimistic that he will see his children again. 
